+### FastAPI (`cd fastapi`)
+
+Requires Python ≥ 3.12 (from `pyproject.toml`).
+
+**First-time setup**
+```bash
+cp .env.example .env             # set SECRET_KEY; CORS origins via settings.cors_origins_list
