-## Tech Stack
+### Cross-track
+
+When changing the data model or API contract, run both tracks' setup-and-test loops:
+```bash
+(cd nextjs && npx prisma db push && npm test)
+(cd fastapi && alembic revision --autogenerate -m "..." && alembic upgrade head && pytest)
